Description: High-performance camera daemon for Raspberry Pi
 ws-camerad is a high-performance multi-consumer camera daemon designed
 for Raspberry Pi with libcamera. It provides:
 .
  * Continuous H.264 hardware encoding via V4L2 M2M
  * Ring buffer for pre-event recording
  * RTSP streaming server
  * Shared memory frame distribution (YUV420 and BGR)
  * Still image capture (JPEG)
  * Video clip extraction
  * Unix socket control interface
 .
 Optimized for low-latency, high-throughput camera applications with
 multiple simultaneous consumers.

