Description: Example clients for ws-camerad
 Example client applications demonstrating ws-camerad usage:
 .
  * still_client - Capture still images
  * clip_client - Extract video clips
  * frame_consumer - Access raw frames via shared memory
  * Python client library and examples

Package: python3-ws-camerad
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         python3 (>= 3.9)
Recommends: python3-numpy
Suggests: ws-camerad
Description: Python client library for ws-camerad
 Python module for communicating with the ws-camerad camera daemon.
 .
 Features:
  * CameraClient - Control interface for still/clip capture
  * FrameSubscriber - Shared memory frame access
  * Response - JSON response parsing
 .
 Example usage:
  from ws_camerad import CameraClient, capture_still, capture_clip
  path = capture_still()
  path = capture_clip(-5, 5)

Package: ws-camerad-dev
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: ws-camerad
Description: C++ development headers for ws-camerad
 Header-only C++ client library for the ws-camerad camera daemon.
 .
 Features:
  * ws_camerad::Client - Control socket client for still/clip capture
  * ws_camerad::FrameReader - Shared memory frame access
  * ws_camerad::Response - JSON response parsing
 .
 Example usage:
  #include <ws_camerad/client.hpp>
  ws_camerad::Client client;
  auto response = client.capture_still();
  auto response = client.capture_clip(-5, 5);
